WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'SevenHex' is a Workbench game in which you try to place 7 pawns
on an hexagonally shaped board, so that none of them are in line,
horizontally or diagonally, with another.

  Have fun!

FEATURES
--------

-Simple installation: just run the game and play!

-Small package, the Lha archive is smaller than 50K, so it
 doesn't take ages to download :)

-The game plays on the Workbench screen and its window is
 resizeable.

